 Life is to live. Life is also to evolve. That which takes form in this universe has a purpose to use space and time to improve itself and evolve into a higher form. That is the meaning of life and the purpose of evolution. - Dr. Stephen T. Chang
  
 <cite><a href="http://thegreattao.com/html/introfounderlaotze.html"> Dr. Chang </a></cite>